WEBVTT

00:11.276 --> 00:13.445
"I may not be the fastest.

00:13.478 --> 00:15.747
"I may not be the tallest
or the strongest.

00:15.781 --> 00:18.518
"I may not be the best
or the brightest.

00:18.550 --> 00:21.286
"But one thing I can do
better than anyone else,

00:21.320 --> 00:25.625
that is to be me,"
which is a poem that you wrote.

00:25.658 --> 00:28.461
Well, finally that's all
you can do, isn't it?

00:28.493 --> 00:30.396
You can do a good
job of doing that.

00:30.428 --> 00:33.632
Do a good job of being me,
being yourself.

00:34.866 --> 00:37.169
That's really all
I ask of myself.

00:38.503 --> 00:40.405
Because as I said,
I wasn't the fastest,

00:40.439 --> 00:43.375
and I wasn't the brightest,
and whatever, you know.

